      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=kt2sfgg1jj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=kt2sfgg1jj]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=l4cq1spspf]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=l4cq1spspf]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=l3d2bgtbpf]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=l3d2bgtbpf]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=oy1t3ugnqp]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=oy1t3ugnqp]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=bhg82jc09p]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=bhg82jc09p]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=fa2m0yz98i]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=fa2m0yz98i]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" width=\"102\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515419489&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562757686/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515419489&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"73\" data-width=\"59\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592838667\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManUniversity_logo.svg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/svg+xml\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562757686\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"f8885aea-9169-44d0-a009-70f2c5db4bb2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515419489&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/RenderManUniversity_logo.svg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515419489&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=59&amp;height=73 1x\" /></span><hr /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/562757686/DemoSign_v01_h264.mov?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515135434&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760\">DemoSign_v01_h264.mov</a></span><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"kt2sfgg1jj\">Project</span></strong>:  RenderMan Demo Sign</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"oy1t3ugnqp\">Created &amp; Written by</span></strong>: Eugene Riecansky</p><p>If you were lucky enough to attend the RenderMan Art &amp; Science fair this year (2025), you would have seen this animation proudly displayed on screens throughout the venue, guiding visitors to our demo pods.</p><p>The lessons below will take you through the steps I used to create this animating neon sign, from modelling and shading to the clever VEX code setup that creatively (randomly) controls the chasing and flashing of the bulbs.  Thank you, Damien, for helping with the VEX code!</p><p>Gloriously rendered in XPU!</p><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/592216069/Neon+Modelling\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592216069\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"modellingButton.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/modellingButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515738026&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562757686/modellingButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515738026&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592576521\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"modellingButton.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562757686\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"3d40478f-ca92-4fcd-a062-a2e8db4f9823\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/modellingButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515738026&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/modellingButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515738026&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManDemoSign-Modelling\"><span data-colorid=\"l3d2bgtbpf\">Modelling</span></h1><p>Learn how I set up a procedural neon-making system in Houdini</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/592183305/Sign+Shading\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592183305\" data-linked-resource-version=\"4\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"shadingbutton.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/shadingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757516927062&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562757686/shadingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757516927062&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592510993\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"shadingbutton.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562757686\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"6d34d233-a90a-4228-a4d2-2b06cd1d4f18\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/shadingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757516927062&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/shadingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757516927062&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManDemoSign-Shading\"><span data-colorid=\"l4cq1spspf\">Shading</span></h1><p>A short lesson showing the process of texturing in Substance Painter</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/591691817/Light+Bulbs\" data-linked-resource-id=\"591691817\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"lightingbutton.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/lightingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515807015&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562757686/lightingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515807015&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592445455\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"lightingbutton.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562757686\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"3a38a72a-119b-43f5-afd5-cb05ec8756bc\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/lightingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515807015&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/lightingbutton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515807015&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManDemoSign-LightBulbs\"><span data-colorid=\"fa2m0yz98i\">Light Bulbs</span></h1><p>Learn the setup techniques used for the various bulbs illuminating the sign.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-right-sidebar\" data-layout=\"two-right-sidebar\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/592019497/Light+Randomization\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592019497\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"randomButton.jpg\" width=\"586\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/randomButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515859110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/562757686/randomButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515859110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"255\" data-width=\"586\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"592773151\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"randomButton.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"562757686\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"16\" data-media-id=\"f0224e39-2061-4d0b-b35f-a2841e36da08\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/randomButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515859110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/562757686/randomButton.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1757515859110&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=586&amp;height=255 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell aside\" data-type=\"aside\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"RenderManDemoSign-LightRandomization\"><span data-colorid=\"bhg82jc09p\">Light Randomization</span></h1><p>Why hand-animate when you can use VEX to do the work for you!</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
